      "comment_id" : 79084733,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "I&#39;ve used the <code>&#39;%&#39; || ? || &#39;%&#39;</code> in PostgreSQL consistently without problems. Against Sybase ASE 15.7 I was getting very weird, non reproducible erratic behavior (from JDBC), sometimes working, sometimes not. After I switched to setting <code>?</code> to be <code>&quot;%&quot;+str&quot;%&quot;</code> I had no more issues."
