      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "@JustLearn: I&#39;m not escaping the prepared statement. I&#39;m escaping the LIKE value. It&#39;s to avoid a mismatch caused by characters considered special to the LIKE clause such as <code>%</code>, <code>_</code> and <code>[</code>. Otherwise when you search for e.g. <code>foo_bar</code> it would incorrectly match e.g. <code>fooxbar</code>."
