    "body" : "<p>Code it like this:</p>\n\n<pre><code>PreparedStatement pstmt = con.prepareStatement(\n    \"SELECT * FROM analysis WHERE notes like ?\");\npstmt.setString(1, notes + \"%\");`\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Make sure that you <strong>DO NOT</strong> include the quotes ' ' like below as they will cause an exception.</p>\n\n<pre><code>pstmt.setString(1,\"'%\"+ notes + \"%'\");\n</code></pre>\n"
