      "comment_id" : 135727724,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "Sadly, not working in H2 2.2.220. A <code>%</code> in the argument given to a prepared statement as shown is interpreted as another wildcard, not as a character that shall be escaped.  For the syntax of the argument to <code>LIKE</code>, see <a href=\"http://h2database.com/html/grammar.html?highlight=escape&amp;search=ESCAPE#like_predicate_right_hand_side\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Like Predicate Right Hand Side</a>."
    } ],
