    "question_id" : 8247970,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>We can use the <code>CONCAT</code> SQL function.</p>\n<pre><code>PreparedStatement pstmt = con.prepareStatement(\n      &quot;SELECT * FROM analysis WHERE notes like CONCAT( '%',?,'%')&quot;;\npstmt.setString(1, notes);\nResultSet rs = pstmt.executeQuery();\n</code></pre>\n<p>This works perfectly for my case.</p>\n"
